Pantry service will be offered on the \*\*1st and 3rd Saturdays\*\* of each month from 8:30 am to 9:30 am. We will do our best to serve all guests, both scheduled and any others during this time.  Scheduled pantry guests should arrive as close to their appointed time as possible in order to avoid clustering on the sidewalk. Everyone is asked to stay at least 6 feet apart.
